Body: ANNOUNCEMENT : MyPitisWallet - BNM Registered!  We are now registered with Malaysia's Central Bank as one of Reporting Agency for Digital Currency Exchanger and activities. Feel free to browse our services offered at www.mypw.io  We offer only services for multi crypto currencies and no program of whatsoever is included. In other words, MLM is prohibited by MPW.  For more information please email us at support@mypw.io  Thank you.

Author: pitiscoin
Title: PitisCoin, The Malaysian Crypto Currency
Body: WHAT IS PITISCOIN   PitisCoin™ is creating an online community for all to facilitate the use of crypto currencies in their lives. We believe that everyone who appreciates advancement are those who will clearly show that crypto currencies are no longer limited to tech people. They will make PitisCoin™ and other coins trendy and profitable.  PitisCoin™ will be used inside the MyPitisWallet to spend or purchase anything in the world. They will also be able to pay each other for favors, and collect funds for philanthropic projects.  The success of this new coin greatly depends on thoughtful emission and distribution strategy. PitisCoin™ is designed for long lasting demand and growth. One billion PitisCoin™ will be emitted to avoid unnecessary scarcity. It is more convenient for the exchange rate to be single digit rather than a few thousands, like Bitcoin’s.  PitisCoin™ community and built-in MyPitisWallet (MPW) (www.mypw.io) wallet will be accessible via its website and mobile apps.
